       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CUSTOMGEN.
       AUTHOR. CASCADE.
       DATE-WRITTEN. 2025-05-10.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 CUSTOMER-RECORD.
       05 CUSTOMER-ID PIC 9(6) VALUE 100001.
       05 CUSTOMER-NAME PIC X(30) VALUE "JOHN DOE".
       05 CUSTOMER-ADDRESS.
       10 STREET PIC X(50) VALUE "123 MAIN ST".
       10 CITY PIC X(20) VALUE "ANYTOWN".
       10 STATE PIC X(2) VALUE "CA".
       10 ZIP PIC 9(5) VALUE 90210.
       01 TRANSACTION-TOTAL PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 ERROR-FLAG PIC 9 VALUE 0.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PROCEDURE.
           DISPLAY "CUSTOMER PROCESSING SYSTEM"
           PERFORM INITIALIZE-PROCESS
           PERFORM PROCESS-CUSTOMER
           PERFORM FINALIZE-PROCESS
           STOP RUN
       INITIALIZE-PROCESS.
           DISPLAY "INITIALIZING SYSTEM..."
           MOVE 0 TO ERROR-FLAG
           DISPLAY "CUSTOMER ID: " CUSTOMER-ID
       PROCESS-CUSTOMER.
           DISPLAY "PROCESSING CUSTOMER: " CUSTOMER-NAME
           IF CUSTOMER-ID > 100000
              DISPLAY "VALID CUSTOMER ID"
              MOVE 1000.50 TO TRANSACTION-TOTAL
           ELSE
              DISPLAY "INVALID CUSTOMER ID"
              MOVE 1 TO ERROR-FLAG
           END-IF
       FINALIZE-PROCESS.
           DISPLAY "FINALIZING PROCESS"
           IF ERROR-FLAG = 0
              DISPLAY "PROCESSING COMPLETED SUCCESSFULLY"
              DISPLAY "TRANSACTION TOTAL: " TRANSACTION-TOTAL
           ELSE
              DISPLAY "PROCESSING COMPLETED WITH ERRORS"
           END-IF
           STOP RUN.
